## from github.com
Make a new pull request
base master from dev
verify the pull request
fix merge conflicts as needed
hit the merge button
delete the branch

## from git cli ### Recommended: save deployment branches in separate directory
pull master
pull dev
merge dev into master
fix conflicts if they exist
push to master

## RELEASE THE CHANGES
watch for pipeline to reach approval stage
inform project owner that the build is awaiting approval
> should tell them the PRs
wait again for pipeline to finish
ssh into box and run the migrations one step at a time
note in the release channel the PR that passed
inform the Devs involved that their builds released
